### =========================================================
### Product Minted Genesis Scenario
### =========================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@contentType = application/json
@brandAccessToken = REPLACE_BRAND_TENANT_TOKEN
@tenantId = REPLACE_TENANT_ID
@groupId = REPLACE_BRAND_GROUP_ID

### 1) Minted (Genesis)
POST {{baseUrl}}/products/tenants/{{tenantId}}/groups/{{groupId}}/minted
Authorization: Bearer {{brandAccessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "serialNumber": "SN-20260303-0001",
  "modelId": "MODEL-001",
  "modelName": "Cyber Sneaker V1",
  "manufacturedAt": "2026-03-03T00:00:00Z",
  "productionBatch": "BATCH-01",
  "factoryCode": "F-KR-01",
  "componentRootHash": "aaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa"
}

### 2) Ledger entries 확인 (consumer 반영 후)
GET {{baseUrl}}/ledgers/passports/REPLACE_PASSPORT_ID/entries
Authorization: Bearer {{brandAccessToken}}

### 3) Ledger verify
GET {{baseUrl}}/ledgers/passports/REPLACE_PASSPORT_ID/verify
Authorization: Bearer {{brandAccessToken}}
